10 AS INTRODUCED
11 A Concurrent Resolution commending and congratulating
the United States of America's Olympic national
12 hockey teams for winning gold medals at the XXV
Winter Olympic Games.
13
14
15 WHEREAS, outstanding athletic achievements reflect great credit
16 upon our nation; and
17 WHEREAS, the Olympic Games are considered the world's preeminent
18 international sporting event; and
19 WHEREAS, the United States of America's men's and women's
20 national hockey teams each achieved victory against Canada; and
21 WHEREAS, both contests were decided in overtime by golden goal,
22 demonstrating exception skill, resolve, and competitive excellence;
23 and
24
